    "text": "Support Local Transportation Act\n\nThis bill revises requirements for the surface transportation block grant program to increase the percentages of program funds required to be allocated to states for each of\u00a0 FY2022-FY2026 for surface transportation projects in\n\n urbanized areas with a population of over 200,000, non-urban areas with a population greater than 5,000, and other areas of the state."
